comment: Monroe (MIL) firms up his position and sets the screen on Schroder (ATL).

Schroder (ATL) makes contact with the ball and any contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) is considered incidental.
Sefolosha (ATL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Sefolosha (ATL) sets the screen on Brogdon (MIL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Hardaway Jr. (ATL) moves his pivot foot.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes body to body contact with Hardaway Jr. (ATL) that affects his SQBR.
Schroder (ATL) makes body to body contact with Brogdon (MIL) that affects his SQBR.

Schroder (ATL) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental contact with one another during the loose ball.

Brogdon (MIL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Schroder (ATL) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
